31:09.459 --> 31:11.709
Oh, really?

31:11.876 --> 31:14.834
"Oh, he is looking at us as always."

31:14.959 --> 31:17.834
"Isn't he feeling desperate always being alone?"

31:17.959 --> 31:19.876
"He will be same as now forever."

31:20.000 --> 31:21.334
"Why is he still living?"

31:26.876 --> 31:28.792
H...Hi, here it is.

31:28.918 --> 31:30.667
I just bought this limited edition, and...

31:30.834 --> 31:31.959
Oops.

31:32.083 --> 31:33.959
Then I'll quit to be a fan of them.

31:34.250 --> 31:35.709
Me too.

31:41.334 --> 31:42.626
That's the reality...

32:02.167 --> 32:04.584
I remember that hair.

32:06.209 --> 32:07.709
Who is he?

32:18.292 --> 32:19.501
By the way,

32:19.792 --> 32:22.584
can I meet Nishimiya again?

32:23.125 --> 32:26.000
She said she feeds carp in the river.

32:26.626 --> 32:29.792
How can I do so by what reason?

32:32.167 --> 32:34.292
Can I see her to apologize what I did?

32:35.876 --> 32:38.417
She said she'll be there every Tuesday.

32:39.459 --> 32:40.792
Am I weird if I visit again?

32:53.083 --> 32:55.125
I'm home.

33:05.584 --> 33:07.000
Sho---chan?

33:08.250 --> 33:09.876
I'm so surprised.

33:10.375 --> 33:11.417
What?

33:13.709 --> 33:16.083
I'm very sorry for what happened in the morning.

33:16.250 --> 33:20.292
I burned money you earned hard.

33:22.125 --> 33:26.334
But I don't want to use any money

33:26.459 --> 33:27.959
you saved to die.

33:29.792 --> 33:31.959
Sorry, I'll save up again.

33:32.125 --> 33:34.167
Thanks.

33:34.292 --> 33:36.334
You can be slower this time, okay?

33:36.501 --> 33:38.792
You are hungry, huh? Let's have dinner.

33:38.918 --> 33:40.667
Hungry!

33:50.626 --> 33:52.542
Tuesday.

33:56.876 --> 33:59.876
Hey you, why don't you lend your bike to me?

34:00.083 --> 34:00.792
Me?

34:00.834 --> 34:03.751
Oh, the guy I remember.

34:04.167 --> 34:07.292
I left something behind. I want to go home to get it.

34:07.417 --> 34:10.250
Huh? What are you saying?

34:10.375 --> 34:12.208
You should use your own one.

34:12.333 --> 34:15.542
I ask you 'cause I don't have my own.

34:16.000 --> 34:17.876
Stop it please.

34:18.000 --> 34:19.000
Hey, don't resist.

34:19.083 --> 34:20.417
Hey, stop it!

34:21.042 --> 34:22.751
Someone please help me!

34:24.333 --> 34:25.458
Someone!

34:25.958 --> 34:27.458
Oh, dear.

34:27.751 --> 34:29.042
Please, please help me! Help! Help!

34:29.167 --> 34:30.667
Shut up!

34:34.042 --> 34:35.918
Stop resisting!

34:36.083 --> 34:38.000
H...hey.

34:38.792 --> 34:40.250
I...I'll lend you my own.

34:40.751 --> 34:44.333
Really!? You are super!

34:48.083 --> 34:50.292
It was ripped off.

34:51.250 --> 34:53.876
Actually, today of all day is Tuesday.

34:54.042 --> 34:57.501
This means I should not see her again?

34:58.209 --> 35:00.417
Of course I still can go on foot,

35:01.000 --> 35:03.667
but it seems as I was advised not to go.

35:04.792 --> 35:06.918
I want a reason.

35:10.876 --> 35:13.959
A smart,

35:14.083 --> 35:16.250
and natural reason to see her again.

35:21.334 --> 35:23.959
"Discount coupon for a brand-new bread ?"

35:25.501 --> 35:26.876
That's it!

35:27.042 --> 35:29.000
Well...Is Nishimiya-san here?

35:29.584 --> 35:30.709
No, she isn't

35:31.626 --> 35:32.667
She is, isn't she?

35:32.792 --> 35:34.501
No, she isn't

35:35.250 --> 35:37.626
Shoko Nishimiya isn't here.

35:38.501 --> 35:39.709
Sorry but,

35:40.083 --> 35:42.876
are you really a friend of Shoko?

35:43.918 --> 35:45.167
Bye.

35:50.083 --> 35:51.292
{\an8}<i>SL: What?</i>

35:51.834 --> 35:53.292
Nothing.

35:54.709 --> 35:56.876
A rat was there.

35:57.042 --> 35:59.167
A big creepy one.

36:02.083 --> 36:04.626
Don't be afraid. It won't come again.

36:12.292 --> 36:14.083
Friend...

36:29.334 --> 36:30.876
Why...is he here?

36:32.209 --> 36:33.792
O--Oh, he is!

36:34.042 --> 36:35.667
Ishida-kun!

36:35.792 --> 36:37.876
Look! Look at this!

36:38.000 --> 36:40.542
A bike! It's yours, isn't it?

36:42.334 --> 36:44.042
Good timing!

36:44.751 --> 36:48.167
It was so lucky that your address was written on the bike.

36:48.542 --> 36:51.709
Wh...where was this bike?

36:51.876 --> 36:53.626
It was abandoned in a rice paddy.

36:54.083 --> 36:56.292
I looked for this all over the time!

36:56.709 --> 36:59.876
I'm glad I got it back to you!

37:07.209 --> 37:08.626
Is something wrong, Ishida-kun?

37:09.792 --> 37:11.918
Well..

37:12.083 --> 37:13.334
Your name?

37:13.459 --> 37:15.792
Oops! I'm Nagatsuka!

37:16.375 --> 37:18.250
I sit just behind you in the class.

37:20.000 --> 37:21.542
Don't you eat some bread?

37:21.959 --> 37:24.959
This is so good, Nagatsuka-kun.

37:25.292 --> 37:27.209
Ishida-kun!

37:27.792 --> 37:29.083
Ishida-kun.

37:30.501 --> 37:32.542
Good morning!

37:32.709 --> 37:34.083
Good morning...

37:36.501 --> 37:37.501
Ishida-kun!

37:38.334 --> 37:40.167
Why don't we hang out after school?

37:40.501 --> 37:42.667
As we are friends now.

37:43.334 --> 37:45.667
Ishida-kun, come here, come here!

38:08.667 --> 38:10.834
What's wrong with you, Ya-sho?

38:12.250 --> 38:13.459
Nothing.

38:13.584 --> 38:14.918
Ya... "Ya-sho"?

38:15.042 --> 38:16.918
Sounds like a "big friend", doesn't it?

38:20.083 --> 38:21.959
Anyway, what are you worrying about?

38:22.417 --> 38:25.876
You can tell anything, 'cause we are real friends.

38:30.125 --> 38:32.459
Nagatsuka-kun,

38:32.834 --> 38:36.000
what is the definition of "friends"?

38:36.334 --> 38:37.918
A kind of license,

38:38.042 --> 38:40.167
or right or something like that,

38:41.000 --> 38:43.542
to become friends with someone.

38:44.459 --> 38:46.125
Hey, Ya-sho.

38:49.542 --> 38:50.751
Give me your hand.

39:04.501 --> 39:06.501
This is friendship.

39:06.709 --> 39:08.959
I think, Ishida-kun,

39:09.083 --> 39:14.209
friendship exists beyond words and logic.

39:14.459 --> 39:17.501
License? No such things are needed.

39:18.000 --> 39:19.209
It's a ridiculous idea.

39:21.709 --> 39:22.709
She is not here.

39:23.501 --> 39:24.501
She is, isn't she?

39:24.751 --> 39:25.751
She isn't.

39:26.083 --> 39:28.626
Huh, who are you anyway?

39:28.751 --> 39:31.125
I'm Shoko's boyfriend.

39:32.667 --> 39:34.959
Oops! ... Dropped.

39:35.125 --> 39:37.751
Haha, that not about me, but a bread.

39:38.209 --> 39:39.959
O...oh, really?

39:40.083 --> 39:42.542
Nishimiya likes younger guys.

39:42.626 --> 39:45.459
I'm a little surprised that.

39:45.584 --> 39:47.542
Okay, then how about giving this bread to her at least?

39:47.667 --> 39:48.417
This is a very good bread.

39:48.542 --> 39:49.542
Hey.

39:49.667 --> 39:54.125
Don't be here again, if you only want to satisfy yourself.

39:57.542 --> 39:59.083
Are you satisfied?

40:00.000 --> 40:01.000
Then bye.

40:02.042 --> 40:03.417
Hey boy!

40:03.542 --> 40:06.334
My friend wants to see Nishimiya-san!

40:06.459 --> 40:09.584
Stop complaining and bring her here right now!

40:09.709 --> 40:11.918
Nagatsuka-kun, why are you here?

40:12.959 --> 40:13.834
I followed you.

40:13.959 --> 40:15.709
Sounds like a behavior of best friends?

40:15.959 --> 40:19.375
Haha, so the friend of a turd had a turd hair.

40:19.501 --> 40:21.083
Hey, you a turd-hair!

40:22.000 --> 40:24.209
Wh---what are you saying?!

40:25.167 --> 40:27.751
Say that again boy!

40:27.876 --> 40:30.042
Turd-hair, turd-hair, turd-hair!

40:30.167 --> 40:32.709
What's happening?

40:32.834 --> 40:33.918
Is that Yuzuru-chan?

40:34.083 --> 40:35.417
Oh, no. They are fighting.

40:36.250 --> 40:38.459
Nagatsuka-kun, Nagatsuka-kun!

40:38.667 --> 40:40.167
Stop it, okay?

40:40.417 --> 40:42.834
Nagatsuka-kun, that's enough, let's go home now.

40:42.959 --> 40:44.334
Nagatsuka-ku...

40:45.292 --> 40:48.125
Oh? Aren't you the boy of the other day?

40:48.584 --> 40:51.167
I--it's not like that!

40:51.501 --> 40:52.626
Nagatsuka-kun, sorry for leaving you!

40:58.542 --> 40:59.751
Oh, crap!

41:00.292 --> 41:02.042
Crap, she found and met him.

41:02.167 --> 41:03.709
Good for you, Ishida-kun!

41:05.918 --> 41:07.334
Hey boy.

41:07.417 --> 41:09.000
You are peeping now, aren't you?

41:09.584 --> 41:11.667
Let me use it now!

41:12.459 --> 41:13.501
What?

41:12.709 --> 41:17.125
{\an8}<i>SL: Long time no see.</i>

41:13.626 --> 41:16.459
Ishida-kun is waving his hands.

41:16.584 --> 41:17.959
Wouldn't it be sign language?

41:17.334 --> 41:19.209
{\an8}<i>SL: Have you been well?</i>

41:18.083 --> 41:19.125
Really!?

41:19.542 --> 41:23.292
Wow, I didn't know he has such a skill.

41:23.417 --> 41:25.667
Hey, can you read their sign language?

41:25.667 --> 41:26.667
Then translate it for me!

41:28.876 --> 41:31.834
Who was that turd-hair just now?

41:29.292 --> 41:31.417
{\an8}<i>SL: I'm glad to see you again.</i>

41:31.667 --> 41:35.375
{\an8}<i>SL: Are you okay leaving your sign language class?</i>

41:33.000 --> 41:35.209
I don't know such turd.

41:35.792 --> 41:37.626
Oops, he was so creepy!

41:37.834 --> 41:39.918
S-T-O-P J-O-K-I-N-G!

41:40.042 --> 41:41.667
Leave me alone!

41:44.042 --> 41:46.125
Be careful not to fall, boy.

41:46.626 --> 41:48.292
"Honestly,"

41:48.959 --> 41:51.876
"I thought I shouldn't see you again."

41:52.667 --> 41:54.918
"The meaning of being friends."

41:55.083 --> 41:59.542
"I've been thinking of it for all these 2 weeks."

42:00.292 --> 42:02.083
"The reason to..."

42:02.834 --> 42:05.542
"see you again."

42:07.542 --> 42:09.417
"I have been looking for it."

42:12.083 --> 42:13.083
Ishida-kun...

42:14.584 --> 42:16.125
"I'm glad."

42:16.292 --> 42:19.417
"I thought"

42:19.584 --> 42:20.792
"the same thing as you."

42:21.751 --> 42:23.292
"It's strange, isn't it?"

42:26.834 --> 42:29.584
Nishimiya, here it is. A bread.

42:29.751 --> 42:30.792
To feed carp.

42:37.209 --> 42:38.876
Is this feeding fun?

42:40.417 --> 42:41.918
Oh, I was just reminded.

42:53.209 --> 42:54.918
{\an8}<i>SL: Thank you.</i>

43:01.292 --> 43:02.292
Nishimiya...

43:02.375 --> 43:04.209
Y...you had better not read it...

43:04.334 --> 43:05.417
so much!

43:15.542 --> 43:17.042
Hey! wait, Nishimiya!

43:21.250 --> 43:22.459
Oh! She fell!

43:22.584 --> 43:24.709
What!? Something happened to Ishida-kun!?

43:24.834 --> 43:25.459
Hey!

43:25.584 --> 43:26.876
Hey, boy!

43:27.626 --> 43:29.626
Oops! Ishida-kun fell to the river!

43:29.751 --> 43:30.751
Why!?

43:31.000 --> 43:31.834
Ouch!

43:31.959 --> 43:33.167
Why you do so!

43:46.751 --> 43:48.250
Oops, what is this creepy thing!?

43:49.751 --> 43:50.209
Nishimiya.

43:58.876 --> 44:00.083
Nishimiya!

44:02.459 --> 44:05.167
Sorry for dropping the notebook.

44:15.167 --> 44:16.918
See you.

44:21.250 --> 44:23.042
{\an8}<i>SL: See you again.</i>

44:31.792 --> 44:34.167
You're stupid, Shoko...

44:42.918 --> 44:44.751
"Any of you got more guts than me?"

44:44.751 --> 44:45.751
"Shoya Ishida"

44:49.209 --> 44:50.751
Stupid!

44:50.876 --> 44:52.459
Did you see this?

44:52.584 --> 44:54.918
Hey, isn't this guy Ishida-kun?

44:56.584 --> 44:58.042
"See you again."

44:59.417 --> 45:00.417
Can I?

45:03.125 --> 45:05.209
Hey.

45:05.918 --> 45:07.667
This is Ishida-kun, isn't it?

45:08.167 --> 45:09.167
This guy.

45:09.501 --> 45:10.501
What?

45:10.626 --> 45:12.334
What's this.

45:17.292 --> 45:20.918
Ishida-kun, come to the teachers' room right now.

45:21.334 --> 45:22.584
"Notice of short-term suspension from school - Shoya Ishida"

45:22.584 --> 45:26.334
"I am very sorry that I jumped into Suimon River from a bridge,"

45:26.459 --> 45:29.000
"where it was prohibited to do so, and..."

45:29.125 --> 45:31.334
"uploaded that photo to the web... "

45:31.459 --> 45:32.959
Hey, Shoya.

45:34.250 --> 45:38.292
Sorry but could you pick Maria back from the nursery?

45:38.417 --> 45:41.042
I'm in a school suspension term and prohibited to go out.

45:41.167 --> 45:44.250
It would be okay if you do it quickly. Please!!

45:44.375 --> 45:45.584
H...hey!!

46:02.375 --> 46:05.792
Maria, let's go home now!

46:05.918 --> 46:07.083
Sho-tan!

46:07.584 --> 46:09.542
Someone is there!

46:15.876 --> 46:16.876
Hey.

46:17.292 --> 46:19.584
Hey, are you okay?

46:22.042 --> 46:25.042
Aren't you Nishimiya's boyfriend?

46:25.375 --> 46:26.375
You'll catch a cold.

46:27.459 --> 46:30.375
Oh, you're the rat.

46:32.209 --> 46:35.292
What are you doing here?

46:37.542 --> 46:38.959
Shoes?

46:42.167 --> 46:43.250
...Why don't you get angry with me?

46:43.959 --> 46:44.959
On what?

46:47.000 --> 46:50.334
It's me who uploaded your photo to the web.

46:50.459 --> 46:52.459
Oh, you did it.

46:54.626 --> 46:55.959
I got it.

46:56.083 --> 46:57.834
I am relieved to hear that.

46:58.292 --> 47:00.125
Why?

47:00.667 --> 47:05.000
I would know the reason why.

47:05.417 --> 47:06.709
Be mad with me.

47:06.834 --> 47:08.626
I cannot.

47:08.751 --> 47:11.459
Originally I am to be blamed.

47:11.792 --> 47:13.167
Sho-tan!

47:13.292 --> 47:15.292
I am hungry!

47:15.709 --> 47:17.083
Okay!

47:17.209 --> 47:19.125
Then I'll go home.

47:19.250 --> 47:20.834
You go home, too.

47:21.459 --> 47:23.792
Haha, you have a kid.

47:25.584 --> 47:27.209
It's not mine, my sis's!

47:37.709 --> 47:38.417
Hey!

47:41.209 --> 47:43.083
Hi Yuzuru-kun,

47:43.459 --> 47:45.501
Please eat enough!

47:45.626 --> 47:46.626
How about sis?

47:47.250 --> 47:48.918
She'll work late today.

47:50.542 --> 47:52.167
Maria, isn't it too hot?

47:52.292 --> 47:54.209
No, it's good!

47:54.334 --> 47:56.751
Yuzuru-kun, why don't you eat?

47:57.584 --> 47:59.250
Hi, Yuzuru-kun!

48:00.709 --> 48:01.709
Please!

48:24.417 --> 48:26.125
{\an8}<i>SL: You should apologize,</i>

48:26.125 --> 48:29.417
{\an8}<i>SL: or I don't need you!</i>

48:31.459 --> 48:32.834
Crap...

48:56.083 --> 48:57.292
What's the matter with you.

48:58.375 --> 49:00.125
I was worried as you disappeared in the night.

49:01.959 --> 49:03.334
Hi, umbrella.

49:05.209 --> 49:06.709
Anyway, use it!

49:06.834 --> 49:08.209
Well, please use it now.

49:09.751 --> 49:10.834
Thank you.

49:11.209 --> 49:12.792
Well, excuse me.

49:12.918 --> 49:14.125
I knew that.

49:16.792 --> 49:18.083
I'll give you these.

49:18.209 --> 49:19.626
These were mine, but

49:20.042 --> 49:22.501
I won't use them anymore. I'll give you.

49:24.876 --> 49:27.959
Why you ran away home?

49:29.709 --> 49:31.959
I had an argument with Shoko.

49:34.250 --> 49:36.167
That's a kind of a typical event

49:36.334 --> 49:39.501
for a long-lasting couple, isn't it?

49:39.959 --> 49:41.042
Yes.

49:41.417 --> 49:43.959
Like that I used Shoko's shampoo without her permission.

49:44.209 --> 49:45.417
I see...

49:45.584 --> 49:47.709
I was said she didn't need me.

49:49.918 --> 49:52.459
Hey, you live together with her!?

49:55.542 --> 49:57.667
Use your umbrella for you.

49:57.792 --> 49:59.083
You have only one, don't you?

50:00.292 --> 50:03.667
It's my mistake I brought only one umbrella.

50:03.918 --> 50:07.792
And I feel sorry for Nishimiya if you catch cold.

50:10.209 --> 50:11.542
Hey you.

50:12.042 --> 50:14.876
What kind of a man you intend to be? A hypocrite?

50:15.959 --> 50:18.501
You feel pleasure taking care of a stray cat?

50:18.709 --> 50:20.542
Or you make fun of doing it.

50:21.167 --> 50:24.209
And you also made fun that she couldn't hear.

50:25.501 --> 50:28.501
Then, now you learned sign language huh?

50:29.000 --> 50:29.709
What's this?

50:29.834 --> 50:32.209
Do you think you have changed to be a good guy?

50:32.709 --> 50:34.918
You are disgusting.

50:38.918 --> 50:40.167
I see.

50:40.626 --> 50:43.626
It's natural you know what I did, hearing from Nishimiya.

50:44.918 --> 50:47.167
Yes. You are right.

50:47.584 --> 50:49.667
I'm the worst human being.

50:50.292 --> 50:52.918
I'm the one who don't worth living.

50:53.959 --> 50:55.209
But, at least,

50:56.042 --> 50:59.626
I thought I didn't want Nishimiya to cry again.

51:00.042 --> 51:03.918
Of course, I have no intention to interfere you two.

51:04.042 --> 51:05.751
Never.

51:06.918 --> 51:08.584
But, actually,

51:08.751 --> 51:10.918
It's an issue of myself, too...

51:26.918 --> 51:27.959
Thanks, it's enough here.

51:31.459 --> 51:32.876
Well..

51:33.501 --> 51:37.000
I'm very sorry that you perfectly believe what I said..

51:37.417 --> 51:38.751
But actually I'm Shoko's...

51:40.459 --> 51:41.459
Understood?

51:49.626 --> 51:50.667
You are her little sis!?

51:50.792 --> 51:51.792
Bye!

51:59.834 --> 52:02.834
Oh, Nishimiya-san's mother...

52:07.584 --> 52:08.792
Hey, let's go.

52:10.083 --> 52:12.709
Hey, it pains.

52:14.417 --> 52:16.626
I'm sorry...

52:20.250 --> 52:22.125
I'm home.

52:22.417 --> 52:23.417
Yu-ju,

52:23.459 --> 52:24.834
Hey, sis!

52:24.959 --> 52:26.959
I'b zorry, I'b zorry!

52:27.334 --> 52:29.417
Me too.

52:30.751 --> 52:33.459
I wanna drink grandma's beefsteak plant juice.

52:34.167 --> 52:35.375
Yuzuru.

52:35.709 --> 52:37.876
Don't be friends with such a guy.

52:38.000 --> 52:39.876
Tell same thing to Shoko from you.

52:42.667 --> 52:45.000
We can decide such a thing by ourselves---

52:45.125 --> 52:46.918
both I and sis.

52:49.000 --> 52:50.292
Hey boy!

52:50.417 --> 52:52.125
Nice to see you!

52:52.250 --> 52:53.584
Why are you here today?

52:53.918 --> 52:55.834
To return his umbrella I lend the other day.

52:55.959 --> 52:56.959
Oh boy.

52:57.042 --> 52:59.167
You are doing a good thing.

52:59.292 --> 53:01.834
Nagatsuka-kun, that child is not a boy...

53:02.292 --> 53:04.751
Little sis of Nishimiya.

53:06.209 --> 53:08.083
Of course, I knew it.

53:13.209 --> 53:16.083
I'm glad to see a friend of my best friend Ya-sho.

53:16.876 --> 53:18.083
He is my classmate,

53:18.209 --> 53:20.918
Na-ga-tsu-ka.

53:26.501 --> 53:28.459
I got my new smart phone.

53:29.167 --> 53:30.167
Well..

53:30.250 --> 53:32.918
Do you have a smart phone too?

