01:36:54.125 --> 01:36:55.125
{\an8}<i>SL: No, I'm okay.</i>

01:36:55.167 --> 01:36:56.501
But...

01:36:59.667 --> 01:37:01.292
{\an8}<i>SL: I'm okay.</i>

01:37:02.542 --> 01:37:03.542
I see.

01:37:03.667 --> 01:37:05.292
See you again.

