01:38:10.083 --> 01:38:11.083
Nishimiya!

01:38:23.042 --> 01:38:23.834
Nishimiya!

01:38:30.792 --> 01:38:31.959
Nishimiya!

01:38:34.417 --> 01:38:35.876
Shoko!

01:38:59.792 --> 01:39:00.918
