01:41:07.209 --> 01:41:08.375
Hi, ma'am.

01:41:08.918 --> 01:41:10.834
Hi, Yuzuru-chan.

01:41:11.542 --> 01:41:12.918
I finally saw you.

01:41:13.250 --> 01:41:15.459
No one answered when I called to the salon, and

01:41:15.584 --> 01:41:17.626
