01:48:03.792 --> 01:48:07.000
Hey, stop it!

01:48:16.292 --> 01:48:17.292
Nishimiya.

01:48:18.417 --> 01:48:19.417
I found you.

01:48:21.167 --> 01:48:22.709
Are you doing well?

01:48:25.250 --> 01:48:26.250
Somewhat--

01:48:26.918 --> 01:48:27.918
strange, isn't it? (laugh)

01:48:29.959 --> 01:48:30.959
